casebody.data:
No. 11-5339 (11A79). Thomas Paul West, Petitioner v. Janice K. Brewer, Governor of Arizona, et al. 564 U.S. 1054, 131 S. Ct. 3092,

180 L. Ed. 2d 914,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5020. July 19, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 652 F.3d 1060.
